node.title: This week on "Face the Nation with Margaret Brennan," April 24, 2022
node.description: Ukrainian Prime Minister Denys Shmyhal, Senator Elizabeth Warren and more appear on "Face the Nation with Margaret Brennan" this Sunday.
node.content: ["Denys Shmyhal - Ukrainian Prime Minister", "Sen.
